            "title": "盤中速報 - 廣穎(4973)股價殺至跌停，跌停價81.2元，成交7,811張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>廣穎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4973:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4973\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4973-TW</a>)23日11:05下跌9元，股價跌停報81.2元，委賣287,000張，成交7,811張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為快閃記憶體相關產品之製造及買賣。記憶體模組之製造及買賣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>廣穎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4973:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4973\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4973-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲15.49%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲9.79%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-626 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-614 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-12 張</li> <li>融資增減：+504 張</li> <li>融券增減：+45 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
